<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_329" id="164r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_329_r2l13"><expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan> <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan> <expan>elt<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> cʒü Pla 
<add><ab facs="#facs_329_line_1588835888638_229">u </ab></add> wen </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_329_r2l14">Edler <expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan> / Als Jr vns <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchrıb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> habt / 
<del rend="strikethrough">von des tages <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan></del> / daʒ Jr </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_329_r2l15">
<del rend="strikethrough">des </del> cʒü dem tage als <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> nu auf nehſten Suntag ſein ſolt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_329_r2l16">nıcht <expan>kume<ex>n</ex></expan> mügt vnd begert / daʒ wir den tag 
<add><ab facs="#facs_329_line_1588786488686_166">
<del rend="strikethrough">ver </del></ab></add>
<del rend="strikethrough"> ſchieben </del> <expan>verſchıeb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_329_r2l17">auf den nehſten Suntag darnach / . das ıſt <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> nehſte Suntag </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_329_r2l18">nach <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>r</expan> frawen tag <expan>Natiuitat<ex>is</ex></expan> ſchierſt / Das wöllen wir </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_329_r2l19">durch <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> willen <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan> gerne tün / vnd den tag alſo ſüchen / vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_329_r2l20">wo wir <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>gnad<ex>e</ex>n</expan> lıeb vnd dienſt <expan>beweiſ<ex>en</ex></expan> möht / Das <expan>tet<ex>en</ex></expan> etc </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_329_r2l21"><expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>f<ex>er</ex>ıa</expan> ıııj̃ . <expan>p<ex>oſt</ex></expan> Egıdij / . </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_329" id="164r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan>
<expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>elt<ex>er</ex>n</expan>, <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> czü
                            Pla<add>u</add>wen </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Edler <expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan>, als ir uns
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> habt, daz ir czü dem
                        tage, als <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> nu <app><note><q type="date">auf nehsten suntag</q>06.09.1411</note></app> sein solt, nicht
                                <expan>kume<ex>n</ex></expan> mügt, und begert, daz wir den tag
                        <expan>verschieb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <app><note><q type="date">auf den nehsten suntag darnach,
                        das ist <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> nehste suntag nach
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan> frawen tag
                            <expan>nativitat<ex>is</ex></expan> schierst</q>13.09.1411</note></app>, das wöllen wir durch
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> willen <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan>
                        gerne tün und den tag also süchen. Und wo wir <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>e</ex>n</expan> lieb und dienst
                            <expan>beweis<ex>en</ex></expan> möht, das <expan>tet<ex>en</ex></expan>
                        etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> iiii <expan>p<ex>ost</ex></expan> Egidii.</ab>
</div>
